Date: Fri, 26 Jun 2026 11:14:27 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] fix(rfork): align seed planner protocol

Use the SEED_KEY-based RFork planner protocol without SEED_RANK for seed lookup and release. Align the example planner and seed protocol client around GET-based add_seed and put_seed endpoints, and add regression tests for the updated headers.

Signed-off-by: yangsonglin13 <yangsonglin566@gmail.com>
